WEBVTT

00:07:58.280 --> 00:08:01.416
I've built a really wonderful fan base,

00:08:01.440 --> 00:08:03.696
really, really sweet and engaged,

00:08:03.720 --> 00:08:06.136
and so I decided to use my social platform

00:08:06.160 --> 00:08:08.216
as kind of this Trojan horse

00:08:08.240 --> 00:08:12.240
wherein I could create a daily practice
of authenticity and vulnerability.

00:08:13.320 --> 00:08:15.000
The response has been incredible.

00:08:15.760 --> 00:08:19.096
It's been affirming,
it's been heartwarming.

00:08:19.120 --> 00:08:22.800
I get tons of love and press
and positive messages daily.

00:08:24.520 --> 00:08:26.440
But it's all from a certain demographic:

00:08:28.200 --> 00:08:29.416
women.

00:08:29.440 --> 00:08:32.135
(Laughter)